Hi friends, thank you for joining us for ElleHacks 2022! This is one of two calendar invites you'll receive. The two sessions will cover the same info, so please pick whichever time is most convenient for you.

This information session will cover the responsibilities of volunteers at the event, as well as how to navigate our event platforms (Hopin, Discord, and Devpost).

This meeting will be recorded and shared afterwards. We're also happy to answer questions via email at info@ellehacks.com.
